## 6. Floating Cards (–ü–∞—Ä—è—â–∏–µ –∫–∞—Ä—Ç–æ—á–∫–∏)

**–ü–æ–ª–Ω—ã–π –ø—Ä–∏–º–µ—Ä HTML:**
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>–ü–∞—Ä—è—â–∏–µ –∫–∞—Ä—Ç–æ—á–∫–∏</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 32px;
        }

        .floating-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 28px;
            box-shadow: 
